        ". Although the standard of the talent on the show was not high, McLurg was impressed with Hornes presentation, especially the way he hosted the programmes quiz; he invited Horne to be the programmes regular quizmaster, a role the latter fulfilled on over fifty Ack-Ack, Beer-Beer quizzes over the next two years. In January 42 he became one of the shows regular comperes and presented the entire show for the first time.     In March 42 Horne was posted to the ": null
